Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:13.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.47,0:00:15.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你朋友找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:22.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友是指…不是初春她們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:24.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.36,0:00:46.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絆理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:48.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.39,0:00:50.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絆理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:53.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絆理…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:55.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是絆理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:01:00.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  得馬上聯絡初春她們才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:34.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:39.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失蹤的十名小孩在MAR的研究室被保護著對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:40.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:42.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:44.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很好嗎初春
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:46.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:50.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這次的事件也跟那個木山有關呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:55.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說為了讓孩子們甦醒  即便學園都市毀滅了也在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:58.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂來也得有個限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:04.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼喚醒枝先他們的方法  特雷斯蒂娜他們會負責尋找的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:05.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:10.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之這就告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:16.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:23.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是在在意木山春生的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:28.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如…從她手裏把孩子們搶過來真的正確嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:30.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:33.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人的判斷是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:35.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子我是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:37.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.83,0:03:39.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:42.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然獨自潛入可疑的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一姐姐大人有什麼閃失…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:46.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:50.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}黑子我…黑子我就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在發什麼呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:51.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:54.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去春上同學她們那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:04:00.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學一定很高興的  來  快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼推我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:05.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…再走快點  春上同學等著我們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:13.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學的…高興的表情…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:17.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:21.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點心跟遊戲  漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:23.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換洗衣服換洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:35.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是等待是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:37.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若不自己去尋找…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:42.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:48.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能救出那些孩子  我什麼都做得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:54.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕與這座城市的所有人為敵  也休想讓我善罷甘休
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:10.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起老師現在我什麼也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:11.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:16.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:24.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友裏有一位叫做春上同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:28.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然才剛剛相識
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:32.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟枝先絆理是青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學是精神感應者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(373,328)\fs18}Telepath
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:38.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在雜亂開放發生的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:38.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:41.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了枝先的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:45.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以因此被懷疑她是不是嫌犯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:50.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此仍然竭力地聆聽枝先的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:53.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  因為枝先找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:55.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:01.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:06.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想春上同學一定非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:08.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:10.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:13.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:26.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上疫苗就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:29.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只需要找到最初樣本…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:33.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣那些孩子們的失控就能平息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:43.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能醒…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:52.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著這些數據去MAR吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:57.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能發揮作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:07:00.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後跟枝先她們見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:07.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家去見一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:08.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去見一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:17.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是…說不過你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:21.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  就因為這樣特意把之前的研究資料給我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:27.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想見一下枝先她們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:29.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾這是不行的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:32.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們被轉移了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:35.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被轉移到比這裏設備更完備的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪裏的設施呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:39.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不能告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.07,0:07:43.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的事情就交給我們這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:47.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MAR會負起責任把他們治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了  春上同學也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:52.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:56.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為那是一直在尋找的很要好的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:58.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是想在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:07:59.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:01.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:03.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:05.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼顏色？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是選的顏色出來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學也好孩子們也好都讓你們見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:10.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:12.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要選黃色嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:14.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:19.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀真可惜是棕色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:22.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很認真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:26.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:28.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特雷斯蒂娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:33.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…反正這種數據起不了什麼作用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:37.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木原所長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:39.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木原
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:41.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:45.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的中間名是  木原哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:48.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特雷斯蒂娜·木原·萊弗萊因
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:51.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:58.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:00.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:01.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是該請回了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情不錯呢  佐天同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:20.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為  現在亂雜開放事件已經解決了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:20.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(305,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:23.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就又能跟大家一起去玩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:27.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢  雖然最近你們都有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:29.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就恢復原狀了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:31.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧  白井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都一如往常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:34.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:44.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  向初春打聽一下春上同學什麼時候能出院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:47.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來才是夏天的精華呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:48.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:49.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:53.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  初春嗎  你現在在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:59.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天…同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:57.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}初春？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:01.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了初春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:02.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:06.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著  光顧著哭怎麼告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:08.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:16.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與亂雜開放相關的資料已經收集好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:16.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(220,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:17.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些全丟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:18.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:21.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才接到MAR的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:23.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂雜開放的事件就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:23.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(260,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都那麼努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:28.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:29.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:31.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只說已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:34.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特雷斯蒂娜·木原
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:41.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的這樣說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼木山春生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:47.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不…知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:49.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點初春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:51.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:52.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:53.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:55.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特雷斯蒂娜·木原·萊弗萊因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與木原幻生有血緣關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:10:58.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他孫女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:10:59.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前木原幻生論文中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:04.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有當時研究所的職員數據
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:08.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  特雷斯蒂娜同時也擔任幻生的研究助手？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:09.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:11.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:13.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:19.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特雷斯蒂娜是能力體結晶實驗的最初受驗者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:27.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著…那麼說來木原幻生把自己的孫女當作了實驗體了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:30.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那孫女則幫助木原
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:33.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後春上同學和留精棄粗的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:33.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Child Error
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:37.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便問我我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:44.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:45.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春別哭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:52.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…春上同學…那麼相信我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:54.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:57.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到該怎麼辦才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:07.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算就這樣一直哭下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:09.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井…同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:13.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以去做的事情還有很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:18.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要什麼時候才能變回風紀委員時的初春
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:18.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:25.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.07,0:12:28.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:32.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要把春上同學他們有可能被轉移去的地點給找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:44.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  御阪同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:48.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:07.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  請用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:08.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:13.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚後同學自那以後一直都在住院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:17.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病情真的那麼嚴重麼  真是令人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:19.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我們一起去看望她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:20.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:30.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管她  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:40.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便一提  孩子們就在那些車裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:42.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去追好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:44.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撒謊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:47.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:49.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有什麼企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:51.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能說是企圖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:54.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木原幻生的孫女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.74,0:13:57.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是能力體結晶的最初受驗者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被自己的爺爺當成實驗體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:06.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  你卻協助幻生的實驗  帶走了孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:09.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:14.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查了不少嘛  聰明的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:19.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊  有誰會一五一十地把別人的問題一一解答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:20.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:24.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是真的那麼想知道的話  就來點硬的瞧瞧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音是…能力下降…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(370,328)\fs18\fsp-0.5}Capacity Down
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你知道這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:36.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:40.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為它就是由我發明的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:45.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發明…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:47.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過將試驗品提供給武裝無能力集團
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:47.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(412,328)\fs18\fsp7}Skill Out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:50.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是搜集了不少資料哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:52.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福  它的性能可是大幅上升了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:56.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是體積會不會變得太大了點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:57.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是武裝無能力集團
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:57.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(351,328)\fs18\fsp7}Skill Out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:00.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要利用方法得當  還是能派上點用場的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:08.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:10.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武裝無能力集團…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:10.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(311,328)\fs18\fsp7}Skill Out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:13.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是你的小白鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別躲開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:23.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  調整還不到位嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:26.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  這樣也挺有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:31.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:34.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量使不出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:38.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧啊  根本就沒能打到這裏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:45.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃吧逃吧  穿著短褲的小姐呦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:52.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在吵些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:58.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…在搞什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…御阪同學？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:16.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的孩子真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:19.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既充滿了正義感又很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:22.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了這樣的你還有你的那些朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:25.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才能找到那些孩子們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:28.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就給你一些獎勵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:32.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的就是將能力體結晶最終完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:40.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓任何人來打擾我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:46.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了一隻頗有意思的小白鼠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:48.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來人把她帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:56.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:17:06.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們明知自己帶走的是我婚後光子的朋友還如此放肆麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:10.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各隊情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:11.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:12.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:13.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We  are  lively
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:13.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:16.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各隊就按照預定…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是藍大理石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:18.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超電磁炮被奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:18.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:19.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:22.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬分抱歉  現在正在周圍搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:23.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會把她找出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:24.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:27.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就在那裏找跟繩子吊死算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:33.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.41,0:17:35.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊吧  御阪學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:37.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有什麼覺得疼的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:41.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:44.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  這都是托我的福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:47.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於我是如何將我的朋友救出險境的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:50.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就那麼想知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:52.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  真是沒轍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來當時我正好在場…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:57.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼  是婚後同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:01.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:04.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人  別突然起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:06.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開  黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:09.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是在這裏悠閒地睡覺的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:12.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點去救春上同學他們的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:18.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擅自潛入了研究所  一時沖昏了頭腦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:22.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才找到的孩子們被特裏斯蒂娜給…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:25.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣大家才被…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:28.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切責任都在我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:31.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  由我來阻止那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開  黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:40.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:46.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在御阪學姐的眼裏能看見什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:50.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見什麼…看見佐天同學啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:07.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:15.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…我不知不覺就看不見了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又給大家添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.98,0:19:20.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什麼麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:27.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  與其分開後擔心  我們寧可在一起經歷苦難
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  這樣才算是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:34.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就是啊  還有我們在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:47.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  下一個是初春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快向白井同學道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:53.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為對白井同學不理不睬的態度向她道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:55.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…佐天同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:56.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:59.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「初春  打了你對不起」  這樣向她道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:05.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  白井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:07.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:11.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  沒有什麼要對我說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:13.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  婚後同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:16.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒關係啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:25.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  特雷斯蒂娜·木原的違法行為已經是有目共睹了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:28.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也知道她所屬的組織有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在要做很多調查…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:33.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有那樣悠哉悠哉的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:34.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:39.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有那麼簡單  我們也有力所不及的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:42.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說要突破極限才有意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:44.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是當時補習的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:47.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一旦放棄了就意味著結束」這話是誰說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:50.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去的話  孩子們會有危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:55.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微給我們點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:01.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警備員那邊把衛星數據傳過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:01.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(210,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:07.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MAR的拖車正行駛在都市高速公路御坊線第18學區的第三交流道上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:12.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坊線…是通往第17學區的道路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.82,0:21:15.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第17學區…為什麼要去那種地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:19.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏有木原幻生所擁有的研究設施
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:25.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  在拖車後面的這輛車  能放大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.13,0:21:26.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:29.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山老師？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.94,0:21:33.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  居然一個人就去了  太獨斷獨行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:38.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人  你這是在等別人吐槽麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:41.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你們還挺像的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.37,0:21:43.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:46.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我該做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:49.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:51.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  快喝這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:54.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚饑何以言戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:55.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我統統吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:56.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.86,0:21:59.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  這份記錄…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:19.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:31.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  要上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:33.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將特雷斯蒂娜打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.56,0:23:36.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了救出春上同學和木山老師  以及
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:38.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們

